# Product Requirements Document: Neon Velocity

## 1. Vision & Objectives
Create a fast-paced, browser-based racing game set in a neon cyberpunk world where players dodge obstacles and overtake rivals as speed intensifies.

## 2. User Stories
- As a player, I want to control a futuristic racer so that I can experience high-speed thrills.
- As a player, I want the game to get harder with each level so that I stay challenged.
- As a player, I want to collect power-ups so that I can gain advantages during races.
- As a player, I want to see my score and rank so that I can compete with others.
- As a player, I want short game sessions so that I can play casually during breaks.

## 3. Feature List

### MVP Features
- Basic racing mechanics (movement, speed increase)
- Obstacle generation
- Power-ups (Turbo Boost, Ghost Phase)
- Score tracking

### Stretch Goals
- Leaderboard system
- AI rival racers
- Customizable vehicles
- Sound effects and music

## 4. Success Metrics
- Players complete at least 3 levels per session
- Average session time is under 5 minutes
- 70% of players return to play again
- Positive feedback on game feel and visuals

## 5. Constraints or Assumptions
- Must run smoothly in modern browsers
- No login or account system required
- Game should be playable with keyboard or touch controls
- Art style must be lightweight (SVG/CSS-based)